	<h2 class="block_header">What to expect when a Health and Safety inspector calls</h2>
		<div class="breadcrumbs"><a href="http://www.tameside.gov.uk/">Home</a>
			 -&gt; <a href="/business">Business</a>
			 -&gt; <a href="/healthsafety/handbook">Health and safety</a>
